      "text": "IAIONE, Fernando Christian, DE NICTOLIS, Elena and FOSTER, Sheila, 2019. The Co-Cities Open Book for Just and Inclusive Cities.  2019. [https://iris.luiss.it/bitstream/11385/195328/1/Open-Book-Final.pdf pdf] [Accessed 15 December 2023]."
